36
00:03:06,061 --> 00:03:07,436
Koliko sam dugo bio vani?

37
00:03:07,437 --> 00:03:08,771
Dvanaest sati.

38
00:03:08,772 --> 00:03:11,358
Isuse. Trebao bih
 češće dobivati batine.

39
00:03:12,192 --> 00:03:14,485
Nisu imali
 Doritose, ali sam dobio...

40
00:03:14,486 --> 00:03:17,154
Oh, snap. Hej. Gospodine Cooper.

41
00:03:17,155 --> 00:03:18,573
Mislio sam da si ga ostavio.

42
00:03:18,574 --> 00:03:19,658
Tata.

43
00:03:20,242 --> 00:03:22,034
- Još uvijek je prilično vani, pa...
